name: Hid User Library
summary: Learn about .MUI_CCCD5AE0 files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: C:\​Windows\​winsxs is used by the system to store components and .MANIFEST files from various Windows updates. The Backup directory within it holds backups of .MANIFEST files in case they become corrupted. It is only used by the system and is not used by Windows Backup to restore lost files.
NOTE: Files in the winsxs directory are important system files that should not be altered or deleted.
